{"tid":1854131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1300港人滯留湖北 有咩說話想同佢哋講？","createTime":"2020-01-31T10:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T12:57:44.000Z","uid":346958,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c4ac748a4f2ed7d105475a6af15aa061900d05","tid":1854131,"uid":346958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"滯留湖北1300港人盼回港　聶德權：需解決交通檢疫<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權表示，收到大約600宗求助，涉及1300名在湖北省的港人，希望協助回港，據駐武漢辦事處了解，求助者健康情況大致良好，已透過衞生署和武漢醫療機構提供健康查詢服務。至於會否包機接香港居民回港，聶德權說當地公共交通停駛，要有可行方法讓港人到集合點等，又說要從公共衞生角度評估，包括需要解決檢疫14日的問題。<br />\n<br />\n2020-01-31 18:13:29<br />\nRTHK<br />\n<br />\n身份認同問題<br />\n我想問佢哋依家覺得自己係香港人定中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc5b65b143efe91c58615ad2766e4edd2a1b454","tid":1854131,"uid":89287,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:34:28.000Z","msg":"咪撚返香港 留係上面死左佢<br />\n唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65045c685d1e28566ef9fd729ca577c7ac9d3bdd","tid":1854131,"uid":37461,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"41b269ea4f7577593ea2c420bf41276992adcd50","tid":1854131,"uid":54295,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"不用怕<br />\n香港是支持你們的<br />\n尤其我們香港警察<br />\n警署會提供食宿給你們<br />\n去到警署說是光頭警長介紹會送果盤的"},{"pid":"f6e7052b89639d7ca7ab0f6af88cc41f79c30a37","tid":1854131,"uid":243175,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"新香港人"},{"pid":"365634700dce85c61877b61784f060f5bc4fbab9","tid":1854131,"uid":117422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"食屎啦"},{"pid":"e7f7cfbb480c29f7f6235f9935e20c9c0a163652","tid":1854131,"uid":315626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img sr